'''罗伯特·安德烈·格林特'''（{{lang-ro|Robert Andrei Glință}}，{{bd|1997年|4月18日||}}）生于皮特什蒂，是一名罗马尼亚男子游泳运动员，主攻仰泳<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rri.ro/en_gb/olympic_profiles_swimmer_robert_glinta-2615322|title=Olympic Profiles - Swimmer Robert Glinta|publisher={{lang|ro|[[罗马尼亚国际广播电台|Radio România Internaţional]]}}|date=2020-04-09|accessdate=2020-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419090141/https://www.rri.ro/en_gb/olympic_profiles_swimmer_robert_glinta-2615322|archivedate=2020-04-19}}</ref>。他在童年时曾接触[[空手道|空手道]]，后来他放弃空手道，改为练习游泳，11岁时首次获得比赛奖牌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gsp.ro/gsp-special/tanarul-saptamanii/micul-phelps-robert-andrei-glinta-e-marea-speranta-a-inotului-masculin-romanesc-388632.html|script-title=ro:Micul Phelps » Robert Andrei Glinţă e marea speranţă a înotului masculin românesc|publisher={{lang|ro|Gazeta Sporturilor}}|date=2013-02-01|accessdate=2020-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208154535/http://www.gsp.ro/gsp-special/tanarul-saptamanii/micul-phelps-robert-andrei-glinta-e-marea-speranta-a-inotului-masculin-romanesc-388632.html|archivedate=2015-12-08}}</ref>。2015年，他进入[[巴比什-博雅依大学|巴比什-博雅依大学]]体育学部就读<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.curier.ro/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=72352&Itemid=418|script-title=ro:Glinţă a plecat la Cluj!|publisher=Curierul|date=2015-10-21|accessdate=2020-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072150/http://www.curier.ro/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=72352&Itemid=418|archivedate=2015-12-08}}</ref>。2017年，他加入美国的[[南加州大学特洛伊人队|南加州大学特洛伊人队]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://swimswam.com/usc-trojans-land-romanian-olympic-finalist-robert-glinta/|title=USC Trojans Land Romanian Olympic Finalist Robert Glinta|work=SwimSwam|date=2017-05-31|accessdate=2020-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531190932/https://swimswam.com/usc-trojans-land-romanian-olympic-finalist-robert-glinta/|archivedate=2017-05-31}}</ref>。

